00080 
00081                         while (fileLen != 0) /* Till the EOF */{
00082

00084                                 fread(frame_len, sizeof(unsigned char),2, file);
00085                                 fseek (file,-4 ,SEEK_CUR);
00086                                 
00087                                 framesize = to_intconvertor(frame_len);
00088                                 line = malloc(framesize*sizeof(unsigned char));
00089                                 memset(line,'\0',sizeof(line));
00090                                 fread(line, sizeof(unsigned char),framesize,file);                              
00091                                 init_cfgparser(line);
00092                                 free(line);
00093                                 fileLen -= framesize;
00094                         }
00095                         fclose (file);
00096 
00097         } else {
00098                         perror (filename); /* why didn't the file open? */
00099         }
